\c 23
\s Imikhosi emisiweyo
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 2 Tshono ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli uthi kubo: Imikhosi emisiweyo yeN\nd kosi\x + 23.4,37; Nani 29.39.\x*\nd* elizayimemezela\x + Eks. 32.5.\x* ibe zinhlangano ezibiziweyo ezingcwele, le yimikhosi yami emisiweyo\x + Eks. 12.16.\x*.
\v 3 Umsebenzi uzakwenziwa insuku eziyisithupha; kodwa usuku lwesikhombisa lulisabatha lokuphumula\x + Eks. 20.9.\x*, inhlangano ebiziweyo engcwele; lingenzi lamsebenzi; lulisabatha eN\nd kosi\nd*ni kuyo yonke imizi yenu.
\p
\v 4 Le yimikhosi emisiweyo yeN\nd kosi\nd*, inhlangano ezibiziweyo ezingcwele\x + Eks. 12.16.\x* elizazimemezela ngesikhathi sazo esimisiweyo\x + Eks. 32.5.\x*.
\v 5 Ngenyanga yokuqala ngolwetshumi lane lwenyanga kusihlwa kuliphasika leN\nd kosi\x + Eks. 12.6,14,18; 13.3,10; 23.15; 34.18. Nani 9.2,3; 28.16,17. Dute. 16.1-8. Josh. 5.10. Ezra 6.19.\x*\nd*.
\v 6 Langosuku lwetshumi lanhlanu lwaleyonyanga kulomkhosi wesinkwa esingelamvubelo eN\nd kosi\nd*ni; dlanini isinkwa esingelamvubelo insuku eziyisikhombisa.
\v 7 Ngosuku lokuqala lizakuba lenhlangano ebiziweyo engcwele; lingenzi lamsebenzi wezisebenzi\x + Eks. 12.16. Nani 28.18,25.\x*.
\v 8 Kodwa lizanikela umnikelo owenzelwe iN\nd kosi\nd* ngomlilo insuku eziyisikhombisa. Ngosuku lwesikhombisa kuzakuba khona inhlangano ebiziweyo engcwele; lingenzi lamsebenzi wezisebenzi.
\p
\v 9 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 10 Tshono ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli uthi kubo: Lapho selifikile elizweni engilinika lona, livune isivuno salo, lethani isithungo sezithelo zokuqala zesivuno senu kumpristi\x + Eks. 23.16,19. 34.22,26. Nani 15.18. 28.26. Dute. 26.1,2.\x*,
\v 11 njalo azunguze isithungo phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + Eks. 29.24.\x*\nd* ukuze lemukeleke. Umpristi uzasizunguza ngosuku olulandela isabatha\x + 22.21; 22.29.\x*.
\v 12 Ngosuku elizunguza ngalo isithungo, nikelani iwundlu elingelasici elilomnyaka owodwa, libe ngumnikelo wokutshiswa eN\nd kosi\nd*ni.
\v 13 Lomnikelo wawo wokudla uzakuba zingxenye ezimbili etshumini zempuphu ecolekileyo ixubene lamafutha, ube ngumnikelo owenzelwe iN\nd kosi\nd* ngomlilo, kube luqhatshi olumnandi; lomnikelo wawo wokunathwayo uzakuba ngowewayini, ingxenye yesine \w yehini\w**\x + 2.14,15,16.\x*.
\v 14 Njalo kaliyikudla isinkwa, lamabele akhanzingiweyo, lezikhwebu ezintsha\x + 2.14.\x*, kuze kufike lona lolosuku, lize lilethe umnikelo kaNkulunkulu wenu. Kuyisimiso esilaphakade ezizukulwaneni zenu, kuyo yonke imizi yenu.
\p
\v 15 Njalo lizazibalela kusukela ngosuku olulandela isabatha, kusukela ngosuku elaletha ngalo isithungo somnikelo wokuzunguzwa; kuzakuba ngamasabatha ayisikhombisa apheleleyo\x + Eks. 34.22. Dute. 16.9.\x*,
\v 16 kuze kufike usuku olulandela isabatha lesikhombisa libale insuku ezingamatshumi amahlanu\x + Seb. 2.1.\x*; khona lizanikela umnikelo omutsha wokudla eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Nani 28.26.\x*.
\v 17 Lethani okuvela emizini yenu izinkwa ezimbili zokuzunguzwa; zizakuba zingxenye ezimbili etshumini zempuphu ecolekileyo; zizabhakwa lemvubelo; ziyizithelo zokuqala eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 23.10.\x*.
\v 18 Njalo lizanikela kanye lesinkwa amawundlu ayisikhombisa angelasici alomnyaka owodwa, lejongosi elilodwa ithole lenkomo, lenqama ezimbili; zizakuba ngumnikelo wokutshiswa eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, kanye lomnikelo wazo wokudla leminikelo yazo yokunathwayo, umnikelo owenziwe ngomlilo, kube luqhatshi olumnandi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni.
\v 19 Lizalungisa njalo izinyane lembuzi elilodwa libe ngumnikelo wesono, lamawundlu amabili alomnyaka owodwa abe ngumhlatshelo\x + 4.23,28. Nani 28.30.\x* weminikelo yokuthula\x + 3.1.\x*.
\v 20 Umpristi uzazizunguza-ke kanye lesinkwa sezithelo zokuqala zibe ngumnikelo wokuzunguzwa phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, kanye lamawundlu amabili\x + 23.11,15.\x*; zizakuba ngcwele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, zibe ngezompristi\x + Nani 18.12. Dute. 18.4.\x*.
\v 21 Lizamemezela ngalona lolosuku; kuzakuba yinhlangano ebiziweyo engcwele kini, lingenzi lamsebenzi wezisebenzi. Kuyisimiso esaphakade kuyo yonke imizi yenu ezizukulwaneni zenu.
\p
\v 22 Lalapho livuna isivuno selizwe lakini, ekuvuneni kwakho ungaqedi emngceleni wensimu yakho; futhi ungabuthi okuseleyo kwesivuno sakho; ukutshiyele umyanga lowemzini. NgiyiN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu\x + 19.9,10.\x*.
\p
\v 23 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 24 Tshono ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli uthi: Ngenyanga yesikhombisa ngolokuqala lwenyanga kuzakuba kini yikuphumula\x + Nani 29.1.\x*, isikhumbuzo sokutshaywa kwezimpondo, inhlangano ebiziweyo engcwele\x + 25.9; Nani 31.6.\x*.
\v 25 Lingenzi lamsebenzi wezisebenzi; kodwa nikelani umnikelo owenzelwe iN\nd kosi\nd* ngomlilo.
\p
\v 26 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 27 Yebo, ngolwetshumi lwalinyanga yesikhombisa kuzakuba lusuku lwenhlawulo yokuthula\x + 16.29,30. Nani 29.7.\x*; lizakuba lenhlangano ebiziweyo engcwele; lizathobisa imiphefumulo yenu, linikele umnikelo owenzelwe iN\nd kosi\nd* ngomlilo.
\v 28 Langalona lolosuku lingenzi lamsebenzi, ngoba kulusuku lwenhlawulo yokuthula, ukulenzela lina inhlawulo yokuthula phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu.
\v 29 Ngoba loba yiwuphi umphefumulo ongazithobiyo ngalona lolosuku uzaqunywa usuke ebantwini bakibo\x + Eks. 30.33.\x*.
\v 30 Laloba yiwuphi umphefumulo owenza loba yiwuphi umsebenzi ngalona lolosuku ngizawubhubhisa lowomphefumulo usuke phakathi kwabantu bakibo\x + 20.3,5,6.\x*.
\v 31 Lingenzi lamsebenzi. Kuyisimiso esilaphakade ezizukulwaneni zenu kuyo yonke imizi yenu.
\v 32 Lisabatha lokuphumula kini; lizathobisa imiphefumulo yenu; ngolwesificamunwemunye lwenyanga, ntambama, kusukela kusihlwa kuze kube kusihlwa, lizagcina isabatha lenu.
\p
\v 33 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 34 Tshono ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli uthi: Ngosuku lwetshumi lanhlanu lwale inyanga yesikhombisa kuzakuba lomkhosi wamadumba insuku eziyisikhombisa eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Dute. 16.13. Ezra 3.4. Neh. 8.14. Zek. 14.16. Joha. 7.2. Nani 29.12. Hez. 45.25. Hos. 12.9.\x*.
\v 35 Ngosuku lokuqala kuzakuba lenhlangano ebiziweyo engcwele; lingenzi lamsebenzi wezisebenzi.
\v 36 Insuku eziyisikhombisa lizanikela umnikelo owenzelwe iN\nd kosi\nd* ngomlilo. Ngosuku lwesificaminwembili kuzakuba lenhlangano ebiziweyo engcwele kini, linikele umnikelo owenzelwe iN\nd kosi\nd* ngomlilo\x + Nani 29.35. Neh. 8.18. Joha. 7.37.\x*. Kungumhlangano onzulu, lingenzi lamsebenzi wezisebenzi.
\v 37 Le yimikhosi emisiweyo yeN\nd kosi\nd* elizayimemezela ibe zinhlangano ezibiziweyo ezingcwele\x + 23.2,4.\x*, ukunikela umnikelo owenzelwe iN\nd kosi\nd* ngomlilo, umnikelo wokutshiswa, lomnikelo wokudla, umhlatshelo, leminikelo yokunathwayo, kube yilokho lalokho ngosuku lwakho\x + Eks. 5.13,19; 1 Kho. 8.59. Ezr. 3.4.\x*,
\v 38 ngaphandle kwamasabatha eN\nd kosi\nd*, langaphandle kwezipho zenu, langaphandle kwezithembiso zenu zonke, langaphandle kweminikelo yenu yonke yesihle, elayinikela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Nani 29.39.\x*.
\p
\v 39 Kodwa ngosuku lwetshumi lanhlanu lwenyanga yesikhombisa, lapho selibuthile isivuno selizwe, gcinani umkhosi weN\nd kosi\nd* insuku eziyisikhombisa. Ngosuku lokuqala kuzakuba lokuphumula langosuku lwesificaminwembili kuzakuba lokuphumula\x + Eks. 23.16. Dute. 16.13.\x*.
\v 40 Langosuku lokuqala zithatheleni izithelo zezihlahla ezinhle\x + Neh. 8.15.\x*, izingatsha zezihlahla zelala, lezingatsha zezihlahla ezilamahlamvu aminyeneyo, leminyezane yemifula\x + Neh. 8.15.\x*, lithabe phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu insuku eziyisikhombisa\x + Dute. 16.14,15.\x*.
\v 41 Lizawugcina ube ngumkhosi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni insuku eziyisikhombisa ngomnyaka. Kuyisimiso esilaphakade ezizukulwaneni zenu; liwugubhe ngenyanga yesikhombisa\x + Nani 29.12-38.\x*.
\v 42 Lizahlala emadumbeni insuku eziyisikhombisa; bonke abazalwa koIsrayeli bazahlala emadumbeni\x + Neh. 8.14-18.\x*,
\v 43 ukuze izizukulwana zenu zazi ukuthi ngabahlalisa abantwana bakoIsrayeli emadumbeni ekubakhupheni kwami elizweni leGibhithe. NgiyiN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu\x + Dute. 31.10,13.\x*.
\v 44 Ngokunjalo uMozisi wabatshela abantwana bakoIsrayeli imikhosi emisiweyo yeN\nd kosi\x + 23.2.\x*\nd*.
